'''Tomás Abdiel Rodríguez Mena''' (born 9 March 1999) is a Panamanian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Monagas S.C.|Monagas]] and [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]].

==Club career==
In 2024, Rodríguez signed for Venezuelan side [[Monagas S.C.|Monagas]]. He was regarded as one of the club's most important players.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jmdeportes.com/futbol/tomas-rodriguez-sigue-con-su-racha-goleadora-en-venezuela/|title=Tomás Rodríguez sigue con su racha goleadora en Venezuela|date=8 April 2024 |publisher=jmdeportes.com}}</ref>

==International career==
Rodríguez is a Panama international. He played his first FIFA matches for the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]] during friendlies against Guatemala and Nicaragua. He scored his first goal for Panama in the [[2025 CONCACAF Gold Cup|2025 Gold Cup]] against [[Guadeloupe national football team|Guadeloupe]]. He also scored against [[Guatemala national football team|Guatemala]] and [[Jamaica national football team|Jamaica]] to make him the first ever Panamanian player to score in their first three gold cup appearances.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tvn-2.com/tvmax/somos-la-sele/tomas-rodriguez-conoce-delantero-convocado-christiansen-espana-galicia-catalunya-monagas-venezuela-nicaragua-guatemala-copa-america_1_2136625.html|title=Tomás Rodríguez: Conoce más del delantero convocado por Thomas Christiansen|date=21 May 2024 |publisher=tvn-2.com}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Rodríguez mainly operates as a striker. He is known for his ball control.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://futbolcentroamerica.com/panama/asi-juega-tomas-rodriguez-el-nuevo-fichaje-en-ataque-de-motagua-video-20230602-FCA-12562.html|title=Así juega Tomás Rodríguez, el nuevo fichaje en ataque de Motagua|date=2 June 2023 |publisher=futbolcentroamerica.com}}</ref>

